$interpreted: Man: Darn it, why did it have to be now...
Man: Thank goodness that you guys saved me. I really don't know how I can express my gratitude.
Irritable Poor Person: That guy is right there!
Man: Crap... I can't get capture here.
Furious Poor Person: Bastard! He got away again!

Furious Poor Person: They are the bandits' comrades!
I saw it with my own eyes; they helped the bandits drive away the monsters!
Irritable Poor Person: We shall seize them and turn them in place of the bandits!
Anxious Poor Person: That's right! Apprehend them!
